    "composer": "Dora Vasconcelos / Heitor Vila-lobos",
    "lyricsHtml": "\nIntro: <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am/E\">Am/E</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am/C\">Am/C</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm/F\">Dm/F</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am9(4)\">Am9(4)</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am7\">Am7</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Acorda, vem ver a lua</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am7\">Am7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que dorme na noite escura</span>\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#°\">F#°</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que fulge tão bela e branca</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B°\">B°</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Derramando doçura</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em/B\">Em/B</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7/C\">F#7/C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Clara chama silente</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ardendo meu sonhar</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am7\">Am7</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">As asas da noite que surgem</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C6\">C6</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E correm no espaço profundo</span>\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Oh, doce amada, desperta</span>\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am7\">Am7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Vem dar teu calor ao luar</span>\n\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am7\">Am7</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Quisera saber-te minha</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am7\">Am7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Na hora serena e calma</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#°\">F#°</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">A sombra confia ao vento</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B°\">B°</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">O limite da espera</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em/B\">Em/B</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7/C\">F#7/C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Quando dentro da noite</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Reclama o teu amor</span>\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am7\">Am7</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Acorda, vem olhar a lua</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C6\">C6</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que brilha na noite escura</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Querida, és linda e meiga</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am7\">Am7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Sentir meu amor e sonhar</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am/E\">Am/E</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am/C\">Am/C</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm/F\">Dm/F</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am9(4)\">Am9(4)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ah!___________________</span>\n",
